name: NEO YC 114: DeepWater
description: One of twenty-seven different cards created for the first ever New Eden Open tournament of YC 114. While not the first ever capsuleer tournament it was the first of its kind to be sponsored by a private media organization and broadcast to a much larger audience. It was also set a new benchmark for prizes in a capsuleer tournament. The New Eden Open broke the tradition of previous capsuleer tournaments by allowing teams to form at will, without the need to be bound to the same alliance. This card represents the following team and sponsor: Team Name: DeepWater Sponsor Name: No team sponsor. Team Captain: HED KANDIR Team Members: Ajwas Tawar Alma Nielly AXBU3PA Ceasari Jerhan Croy Karl XI Lsd777 MAFIOZOxNAHODKA MaxKalkin mikecher MonkeyDrummer sl Garsk Susen Kelven Trash Ice vNSOv Wiker Can you collect them all?
